subject: You missed it!
body: Catch our big announcement below. We’re wrapping up X4, the Experience Management Summit of the year. Keep reading to catch a day behind the scenes, and our attempt at building our AI career opportunities boxes!Hot Jobs 🔥Find our hottest jobs below, or check out areas of the business we're hiring for the most: Sales | Customer Success & Services | EngineeringFederal Account Executive - DHS AccountWashington, District of Columbia, United StatesAPPLYEdge Software Sales Enterprise Account Executive (AE)United States (Remote)APPLYSenior Product Security Engineer - ProvoProvo, Utah, United StatesAPPLYPrincipal Experience DesignerProvo, Utah, United StatesAPPLYTransformation Process DesignerProvo, Utah, United StatesAPPLYExecutive AssistantMexico City, MexicoAPPLYEdge Value ManagerProvo, Utah, United StatesAPPLYTechnical Success Manager, ResearchMexico City, MexicoAPPLYPartner Sales ManagerTokyo, JapanAPPLYResearch Manager - JapanTokyo, JapanAPPLYPartner Marketing Manager, JapanTokyo, JapanAPPLYThe future for Experience Agents is so bright......we might have to wear shades! 😎At X4, we shared more about the launch of Experience Agents — our groundbreaking AI-powered autonomous agents that are reshaping how organizations connect with customers and employees. These agents are the secret ingredient to building deeper, more meaningful connections and stronger customer relationships.Missed X4 this year? No worries! Catch the content here. The journey will continue with X4 2026 in Seattle!Go behind the scenes of X4 with TaylorFollow Taylor, a Technical Support Manager here at Qualtrics, as she navigates the buzzing energy of the X4! From helping customers find new ways to use our product to celebrating her community at an employee event by night, Taylor’s day is all about adding value for the customer. 🤩Ready to see how we blend passion with purpose? Catch Taylor behind the scenes at X4!Life is like....a box of opportunitiesWe gave the AI Barbie Box trend a shot. 💅Whether you’re a Machine Learning Engineer crafting mind-bending algorithms, or a Sales Development Representative forging connections—your dream job could be waiting for you in our box of opportunities!Join the trend by creating your own AI-inspired action figure. 👇Upload your photo with the below [filled-in] prompt, in your AI of choice:Create an action figure toy based on the person in the photo. Next to the figure, there should be the toy’s equipment, each in its blisters.N/B: Don’t repeat the equipment under any circumstances![EQUIPMENT 1: e.g. cup of coffee, nike shoes, laptop][EQUIPMENT 2][EQUIPMENT 3][EQUIPMENT 4][EQUIPMENT 5]The card holding the blister should be [INSERT COLOR]. Also, on top of the box, write "[NAME]" with "[SUBTITLE]" in a smaller font underneath that. The figure and equipment must all be inside blisters. Visualize this in a realistic way.Like this newsletter? Tell us what you want to see more of here.Keep Up with Life at Qualtrics© 2023 Qualtrics®Be sure to add opportunities@jobs.qualtrics.com to your contacts so you don't miss anything from Qualtrics Life Insiders!If you no longer want to receive communications regarding Qualtrics Life Insiders click here: unsubscribe Please know that unsubscribing from Qualtrics Life Insiders will not prevent you from receiving communications regarding your candidacy and you may still receive job alerts and communications from other parts of the Qualtrics business. You can control all of your job related communications preferences here.
